cc:Work.dc:title: Cool Asian Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: This is from an old public domain Japanese book. The book was boring but the frame was awesome! The whole top of the frame was damaged beyond use, so I fixed that up. The left side was damaged too and I could have fixed it... but I liked the organic feel of a broken side. With computers everything is becoming perfect and geometric. I enjoy the living real feeling of the past...
